{"tid":2515401,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"妹子想談職場戀愛扮OL潛入男友公司","createTime":"2021-05-04T03:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T04:21:53.000Z","uid":141060,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"61c26463769195c12de2dfd8af61bc3628ab5be1","tid":2515401,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:11:33.000Z","msg":"只要當事者都是在同間公司任職，無論是否同處於同部門都屬於職場戀情。<br />\n<br />\n鬧不合搞到雙雙離職的案例也很多，很多公司會禁止員工發生辦公室戀情，但也不是說在辦公室尋求邂逅就是搞錯了什麼。<br />\n<br />\n但日本有一推友「倉持 リネン@linenkuramochi」，本身是畫家，但她非常想要跟男友談一場職場戀愛， 所以刻意喬裝打扮，跑到男友公司約個會來滿足自己心中那份抑制不住的心情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSmFepa1vCJzDfBVXwrpimN53CS3qRLARR8vFWYRNuwsV?filename=47A4fjW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47A4fjW.png&h=9971dacd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n推友為了能模擬職場戀愛，特別把當初上大學時穿的制服拿出來，出發前做了便當，通勤兩小時跑到男友的公司，利用中午吃飯時間與男友午餐。<br />\n<br />\n沒有你們想的後續，妹子假裝完自己談完了辦公室戀情後，就心滿意足的回家了。<br />\n<br />\n為了讓這場模擬劇處處細節到位，她甚至製作了員工識別證&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUHPvC5fkcEoiRPai34Tv1i65VVogXzexqeCSz7rPN5Ko?filename=1yKgQTs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yKgQTs.jpg&h=3daf9c4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea97097c08446f21341f97a011efeaabea2b49a0","tid":2515401,"uid":200496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:12:22.000Z","msg":"其實幾cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4742cd98a0d919e6b0c4d45c30ed2fe4bcbc4abb","tid":2515401,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58550fd4f42ee6e3dca89a2270e04646e6d571c5","tid":2515401,"uid":180173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:13:19.000Z","msg":"其實即係著住ol裝同男女食飯"},{"